                <note rend="inline" type="source">550.S1/678: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in France</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Marriner</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1933-04-21T18:00:00-05:00"
                            >April 21, 1933—6 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>99. For Norman Davis. Your 177, April 21, 5 p.m. April 29th seems feasible and if
                    in the meanwhile the President and Mr. MacDonald, who will arrive here this
                    afternoon, have any suggestions to make you will be immediately advised.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
